{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first thing we saw-- of course there were rumors-- but the first thing I saw was the guards starting to get in their trucks and some of them run away by foot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as-- as that happened, we broke into the armory and helped ourselves to some of their rifles and started chasing them and shooting at them, and they were running away.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the prisoners-- I myself didn't know how to work a rifle, but I learned quickly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was on May 2, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I-- I have a-- what I call a born-again birthday party every year on May 2 or close to it, as long-- the closest Sunday to it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have a great big born-again birthday party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I invite all my friends here in town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not-- not necessarily survivors of concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those people are too dour for my taste.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we just celebrate with food, drink, and music.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This isn't-- this isn't something that I particularly like to talk about, but quite a few guards were killed, and some of the prisoners were killed, too, because the guards were shooting back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we saw a Jeep with American soldiers with an American flag ride down the road.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they saw us, we looked-- we looked like a bunch of hooligan terrorists.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just turned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We started waving at them and running towards them, and they just turned the Jeep around and took off, which was just as well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They may have been overwhelmed by our kindness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For some reason my buddy and I separated, and I latched onto two other guys, and we started going around in the neighborhood and eating.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
